Title: Log Viewer
Description: This project is a winforms application that helps you view various server log files.  There are many applications that do the same work, but I wanted to create an extensible log viewer that allowed the user to control what they were viewing.

Project Description
This project is a winforms application that helps you view various server log files. There are many applications that do the same work, but I wanted to create an extensible log viewer that allowed the user to control what they were viewing.
